<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 32 (July 9th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Burden of Knowledge (W)</B></li><ul><li>Fixed a bug where this ability's slow proc from basic attacks was slowing less than intended at ranks 2-5.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 31 (June 17th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Chains of Fate (Q)</B></li><ul><li>The cooldown of this ability has been reduced to 13/12/11/10/9, down from 15/14/13/12/11.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 27 (March 17, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Burden of Knowledge (W)</li><ul><li>Fixed a bug where the magical damage done by this ability would not proc generic non-basic/non-ability specific damage triggers, such as Judgement's Magic Shred or Will Thief's Magic Resistance steal.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Chains of Fate (Q)</li><ul><li>The range of this ability has been increased by 11%.</li><li>The Power ratio of this ability has been reduced to 0.6, down from 0.75</li></ul><li>Burden of Knowledge (W)</li><ul><li>The passive on this ability will no longer knock up Shapers when struck. Instead, it will now slow the target by 40/50/60/70/80% decaying over 0.5 seconds.</li></ul><li>Great Rift (E)</li><ul><li>The range of this ability has been increased by 11%.</li></ul><li>Final Chapter (R)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 2750, from previous value of 3040.</li><li>The Power ratio of this ability has been reduced to 0.8, down from 1.25.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 16 (Oct 31, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Now receives a buff icon that indicates the time remaining to reactivate Final Chapter (R) after dealing a killing blow with this ability.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 12 (September 26, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Final Chapter (R)</B></li><ul><li>The Power scaling on this ability has been reduced to 1.25, down from 1.5.</li></ul></ul>